• Work in a challenging and pleasant business environment;  

Your responsibilities will be related with:  

• Tracking the cases and CSAT results following the processes;  
• Follow up with the customers until problem is resolved;  
• Monitor the relevant queues;  
• Follow up on cases assigned, creation of new cases according to the
processes;  

To be suitable candidate you need to possess:  

• Fluency in Hungarian;  
• Good level of English language;  
• Excellent customer handling skills;  
